{"tid":1401691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正常打仗被圍，我方人數佔優，上策係撤退，下策係束手就擒，中策係攬炒","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:05:08.000Z","uid":30791,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0e5c3ed5aed76287eb75726e3a2066c2ea5d5ab6","tid":1401691,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過而家唔係打仗 而家呢個勢 要贏呢場仗唔洗攬炒<br />\n我誠懇呼籲大家 唔好攬炒<br />\n前線請留住有用之軀 將來為港效力</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8ca31ec06b443fbd0183a94c5f72a90d2695d323","tid":1401691,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4b7577636826e4ea30ffaa71d99ec7ad10d8fce","tid":1401691,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"可以提出建議，但係絕對唔可以鬧唔可以怪責，更加<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔應該串唔應該冷嘲熱諷，咁樣只會破壞關係同信任</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">大家都想贏，只不過思考方式不同</span><br />\n每個人都有優點缺點<br />\n你覺得前線蠢，咁你有無佢地既勇氣去前線？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可能佢地做左一啲你地覺得絕對唔理智既行為，但係大家都應該以團結為前題，去解決依個問題，而唔係返返2014年互相指責</span>"},{"pid":"6fa8f935cd889b698f634ff0d63226810157d831","tid":1401691,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd33d0c9267a753783cbf36e426d6625f05630fc","tid":1401691,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f0ba5557e8462995ef372c630cb989c4